name: Jumpy Bird (StinkerFrog)
description:
You are a cute little chicklet who wants to fly, but you're too impatient to learn how.

Luckily there's some convenient floating islands nearby. There's also a poacher or something I guess.

Jump on floating islands and dodge the bullets!

a/d or arrows to move, space to jump.
